### Describe the bug

### Description:
I am encountering an issue where the `onclick` event in my `nav.razor` component ceases to function after adding the `hero.razor` component to my main layout. The issue also seems to be connected with the use of arbitrary values in Tailwind CSS, specifically when a forward slash (`/`) is included.

